{"word":"G1854 - ἔξω - éxō - ex'-o - Away","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔξω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">éxō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Away</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வெளியே, புறம்பே - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"without, out of doors"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a>; <i>out</i> (<i>side</i>, <i>of doors</i>), literally or figuratively: - away, forth, (with-) out (of, -ward), strange.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}